Summary: Saucer shaped objects in the sky above Waikiki Beach.
divs: Sighting DetailsI stayed in an Oceanfront hotel room across from Waikiki Beach and was taking photos of the sunset from my balcony. I noticed these two objects in the sky months later when looking at the digital pictures. I tried zooming in on the objects and it doesnt look like a bird or an airplane at all. All I can say is it appears to be an unidentified flying object...
